public abstract class BlocksAttacksComponent<I extends AbstractItemStack<T>,T> extends Object implements SerialComponent<I,T>
BlocksAttacksComponent - When present, this item can be used like a Shield to block attacks to the holding player. Added in MC 1.21.5
